text: Hackensack is a city of Bergen County in the state of New Jersey in the United States. It is the county seat of Bergen County. Almost 46,000 people were living in Hackensack as of 2020. == References == == Other websites == * Hackensack official website Category:Cities in Bergen County, New Jersey Category:County seats in New Jersey Category:1921 establishments in the United States
